caption:
I love to be around women! Even when women who've never met before, they come across eachother feel they've always known one other and that's how womanhood care, nurture & understand is common! That energy is contagious (with right women, it's always in a good way!) 

@herfocuss you guys nailed it. Directing a beautiful community towards upskilling, learning, living & existing around each other without judgements. Thank you for having me over! 

Women's day now is not a celebration but slowly turning into survival guide.. may womanhood ALWAYS stand by eachother and make it a better place one day at a time🩷🌻✨

Kashi clarified my anatomy of life & volatility of emotions.. isn't that beautiful? And also.. it's that time of the year we travel again! Maybe soon.. or maybe a little later 🩷☀️🌻✨

